@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nPOST /api/users/register" as API
participant "Database\nTable: User" as DB
User->UI: Enter registration information
UI->API: Submit registration request
API->DB: Validate and store user data
DB-->API: User account created successfully
API-->UI: Return registration result
UI-->User: Display registration confirmation

@enduml
